title: Naya jeevan ko hamein de Prabhu
lyrics:
Naya jeevan ko hamen de Prabhu
Tere pyar ko bhi de -2
Jaise ham tere saath chalun -2
(A)
Ham hain paap se doobe hue insaan
Karo tum hamen paritran -2
Jaise ham ho saken tera (insaan-3)
(B)
Jab tum is duniya mein aoge
Sach-jhooth ka insaaf karoge -2
Jaise ham ho saken tera (insaan-3)
